I think I've tracked it down to here: https://github.com/gorilla/schema/blob/master/decoder.go#L194

seems like if the fields in the struct are lowercase, thus unexported - CanSet returns false

```
query := struct {
	FromImage string `schema:"fromImage"`
	Tag       string `schema:"tag"`
}{}
```

seems like this should fixe it
